    Efficient Window Management

    Reduce mouse movement and eliminate the frustration of aiming for tiny window buttons with these powerful features.

    Minimize from Dock

    Click an app's dock icon to minimize it, and click again to bring it back. Simple and intuitive.

    Quick App Switcher

    Hold the right mouse button or 'fn' key and scroll to instantly switch between your open applications.

    Intuitive Window Control

    Right-left-click or double-right-click to minimize, or hold the right button and tilt the wheel to halve windows.

    Enhanced Stage Manager

    Found it hard to get used to stage manager? Try using it now with Click2Minimize and all gestures enabled - you'll discover how intuitive it becomes.

    Switch Workspaces

    Effortlessly switch between your macOS workspaces by tilting the mouse wheel left or right.

    And So Much More...

    Middle-click to close app, replace Finder click with 3rd-party alternative app, move windows to the next screen, and many more...
